metadata.name: #01 Golden Artifact
metadata.description:
#01 Golden Artifact 

My very first piece created as an NFT. 

Signed by aching hand, Golden Artifact twists and turns seem to lead you on a journey of discovery and good fortune, guiding you towards a prosperous future.

Imbuing this piece with gold unicorn blood is a potent symbol of wealth and abundance. Holding this NFT increases the users ability to unlock hidden secrets and mysteries on their journey through Web3.


Use it well.
